OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1772019654
OL,3,CCourt to decide today if legal
OL,4,Cchallenge against migrant camp can
OL,5,Cproceed
OL,7,FCampaigners in East Sussex will find
OL,8,Fout today whether they have been
OL,9,Fgranted permission to bring a judicial
OL,10,Freview against the government over the
OL,11,Fuse of a former army barracks to house
OL,12,Fasylum seekers.
OL,14,FThe High Court is expected to rule on
OL,15,Fwhether a full legal challenge can
OL,16,Fproceed against the Home Office's
OL,17,Fdecision to use the Crowborough
OL,18,FTraining Camp as temporary
OL,19,Faccommodation for up to 600 single men.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
