PN,41402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1772019654
OL,3,CCourt to decide today if legal
OL,4,Cchallenge against migrant camp can
OL,5,Cproceed
OL,7,FThe site, which began housing its
OL,8,Ffirst residents in late January, has
OL,9,Fbeen the subject of fierce local
OL,10,Fopposition. Last month, thousands of
OL,11,Fpeople took to the streets of
OL,12,FCrowborough in what was described as
OL,13,Fthe "loudest protest yet," following
OL,14,Fthe arrival of the first 27 men at the
OL,15,Fcamp.
OL,17,FLocal campaign groups and residents
OL,18,Fare seeking a judicial review on
OL,19,Fseveral grounds, arguing that the site
OL,20,Fis "wholly unsuitable" for large-scale
OL,21,Fasylum accommodation.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1772019654
OL,3,CCourt to decide today if legal
OL,4,Cchallenge against migrant camp can
OL,5,Cproceed
OL,7,FConcerns raised by the community
OL,8,Finclude:
OL,10,FThe Home Office, however, maintains
OL,11,Fthat using military sites is a
OL,12,Fnecessary step to end the use of
OL,13,F"costly" hotels for asylum seekers.
OL,15,FIn its official factsheet, the
OL,16,Fgovernment stated the site provides
OL,17,F"basic, safe, and resilient"
OL,18,Faccommodation and is designed to be
OL,19,Fself-sufficient to minimize the impact
OL,20,Fon the local town.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
