FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1772019654
OL,3,CCourt to decide today if legal
OL,4,Cchallenge against migrant camp can
OL,5,Cproceed
OL,7,FThe tension in the town reached
OL,8,Fboiling point in late January, with
OL,9,FSussex Police making several arrests
OL,10,Ffollowing reports of disorder outside
OL,11,Fthe barracks.
OL,13,FIf the judge grants permission today,
OL,14,Fa full judicial review hearing will be
OL,15,Fscheduled for a later date. This could
OL,16,Fpotentially lead to the suspension of
OL,17,Ffurther arrivals at the camp or a
OL,18,Ftotal reversal of the Home Office's
OL,19,Fdecision.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
