PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1772019654
OL,3,CCourt to decide today if legal
OL,4,Cchallenge against migrant camp can
OL,5,Cproceed
OL,7,FIf the application is refused, it will
OL,8,Fbe a significant victory for the
OL,9,Fgovernment's "military site" strategy,
OL,10,Fwhich also includes controversial
OL,11,Flocations in Essex and Lincolnshire.
OL,13,FThe Home Office says it has 24/7
OL,14,Fsecurity on-site and that residents
OL,15,Fare required to sign in and out,
OL,16,Finsisting that "public safety remains
OL,17,Four first priority."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/5
